item.title: CVE-2023-2482|2024-08-02T06:26:09.239Z -- unknown -- responsive%20css%20editor
item.description: The Responsive CSS EDITOR WordPress plugin through 1.0 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high-privilege users such as admin.
